---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 138
By: Abu 'Uthmân al-Hayrî al-Nisâbûrî
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Renunciation-Detachment=Detachment From Place and
    Conditions
---
Man is perfect only when bestowal and denial, humiliation and honour, have
become alike in his heart.
